Subject: [R-meta] Meta-Analysis using different correlation coefficients
In-Reply-To: <mailman.3835.1882.1644389692.912.r-sig-meta-analysis@r-project.org>
References: <mailman.3835.1882.1644389692.912.r-sig-meta-analysis@r-project.org>
